tool_description: Six fully configurable AI models to create images and art from text descriptions. Most of them are based on Stable Diffusion.
name: Image Generator Using Text Descriptions - Fast & Cheap
title: Image Generator Using Text Descriptions - Fast & Cheap
tool_name: Image Generator Using Text Descriptions - Fast & Cheap

api_list.name: Group 2: Lykon DreamShaper
api_list.description: Generate an Image from Text Description. This API endpoint returns an image in PNG base64 format. To easily visualize the generated image, please refer to the 'Tutorials' section.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://image-generator-using-text-descriptions-fast-cheap3.p.rapidapi.com/v1/inference/Lykon/DreamShaper"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "image-generator-using-text-descriptions-fast-cheap3.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
